{
  "stem": "26672.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And eventually, after a while, I heard there was a camp nearby.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "An aunt of mine was in it-- my father's sister, named Tzipporah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And a cousin of mine named Chaim was there, the one who jumped from the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "How they got to that camp, I don't know, but they were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And this is nearby an airfield, an Air Force Base.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I knew which sort of direction they were coming from work or to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And one day, I managed to-- to get near and lie in hiding till they passed through and joined-- and joined that group going back into-- into the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And my aunt-- I mean, the people-- most of the people knew me, because they were local people, all local, either Deblin or Ryki people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There were quite a few from Ryki in those days, in that camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they contact my aunt and they told her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then she hid me in her barrack, the women's barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There were barracks for women and barracks for men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "She hid me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And then, eventually, there was a registration in the camp, and I stood up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "There was quite a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I was registered as one of the inmates in the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So I was-- I didn't have to hide anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You manage to find only from farms, whatever you could find.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At night, to get into a farm and find some raw fruit, vegetables, whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't think they were too bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was near our hometown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was only surrounded by barbed wire and with a few Germans, about.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- I remember the gate, a barbed wire gate.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
